title: John Fogerty - Loma Prieta Relief Show Oakland  1989 ak320
description:
John Fogerty - Loma Prieta Relief Show Oakland  1989 ak320

Minutes before the scheduled start of the third game of the 1989 World Series in San Francisco, a magnitude 6.9 earthquake rocked the California coast from Monterey to San Francisco. Centered near Loma Prieta peak in the mountains south of San Jose, the quake killed 63 people and caused an estimated $10 billion in property loss. 

It was the first large jolt in the region since the Great San Francisco Earthquake of 1906 (magnitude 7.8). Although the Loma Prieta earthquake struck on the periphery of the region–more than 50 miles from San Francisco and Oakland–it exposed the vulnerability of the region in future quakes, which will be larger and closer to its urban core. 

And analogkid was there in Oakland for the event. (Not this concert but the Quake) It was not fun but I was not bored either.
But thats a story for another time.... Were here to share this show from John Fogerty who lives in the Bay Area .(Berserkley)
